ActFirearms Act
SubjectOrder Entering into Contribution Agreements with the governments of the provinces
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Public Safety and Emergency Preparedness to ENTER INTO AGREEMENTS with the governments of the provinces that provide for PAYMENT OF COMPENSATION in respect of administrative costs actually incurred by the provinces in relation to processing licenses and auhorizations and applications for licenses and authorizations under the FIREARMS ACT.
